DESCRIPTION:When a young mom's surrogate disappears days before the due dat
	e\, the ensuing search uncovers dark truths and the power of a mother's lo
	ve.\n\nThird Place Books welcomes bestselling author and Killer Women podc
	ast host Danielle Girard to our Ravenna store for a conversation about her
	 new book Pinky Swear — a thriller about motherhood\, friendship\, and how
	 well we can ever really know another person. She will be joined in conver
	sation by Danya Kukafka\, author of Notes on an Execution and Girl in Snow
	.\n\nThis event is free and open to the public. For important updates\, RS
	VP is highly recommended in advance. This event will include a public sign
	ing and time for audience Q&A. Sustain our author series by purchasing a c
	opy of the featured books!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detail
	s/danielle-girard-with-danya-kukafka-pinky-swear/18422937/2026-04-06T00
