UID:YuImrMp81crdlpE40jt7y
SUMMARY:Campus Council on Planning and Budget (CCPB) Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260406T054308Z
DTSTART:20260408T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Location Type: Online Event sponsors: UW Bothell General Facult
	y Organization Accessibility Contact: dawn3@uw.edu\n\nIf you would like to
	 attend\, please email Dawn Moncalieri\, GFO Progr am Coordinator\, at  da
	wn3@uw.edu to request the zoom link.\n\n\\*\\*\\*AN AGENDA WILL BE ADDED H
	ERE ONE WEEK PRIOR TO MEETING\\*\\*\\*\n\nThe UW Bothell Campus Council on
	 Planning and Budgeting \\(CCPB\\) serves as an advisory board to the UW B
	othell Executive Council on long-range strategic planning\, preparation of
	 budgets\, a nd distribution of funds as they relate to issues of concern 
	to faculty. This council meets monthly.\n\nTo learn more about CC PB\, see
